	 <CRLF>
	 <CRLF>
	 <SAY-THE ,MAGICK-SHOPPE>
	 <TELL " stands nearby." CR>>

<ROUTINE DESCRIBE-SIGN ()
	 <TELL 
"A curiously painted sign over the " D ,HOUSE-DOOR " reads, \"Ye Olde "
D ,MAGICK-SHOPPE ".\"" CR>>

