<ROUTINE SHOPPE-DOOR-F ()
	 <COND (<AND <VERB? OPEN MOVE PULL PUSH>
		     <EQUAL? ,PRSO ,SHOPPE-DOOR>
		     <NOT <FSET? ,SHOPPE-DOOR ,OPENBIT>>>
